---
import { FIVE_MECHANISMS } from '@/data/chain';
---
<section class="section wrap" id="mechanisms" data-screen-label="02 mechanisms">
  <div class="sec-eyebrow" data-reveal>
    <span class="num">§ 02</span>
    <span>FIVE MECHANISMS</span>
    <span class="rule"></span>
    <span>WP §3–§10</span>
  </div>
  <h2 class="sec-title" data-reveal>
    How the protocol <span class="it">actually works.</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="sec-lede" data-reveal>
    Five mechanisms, each specified to component level in the whitepaper. No novel
    cryptography. The contribution is the synthesis.
  </p>

  <div class="mech-grid" data-reveal>
    {FIVE_MECHANISMS.map((m) => (
      <div class="mech">
        <div class="num">§ {m.num}</div>
        <div class="name">{m.name}</div>
        <div class="desc">{m.d}</div>
        <div class="meta">{m.meta}</div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
